msgstr "Leer la guía de resolución de problemas"

#: .tmp-wporg/structura/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:131
#: plugin/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:131
msgid "MySQL packet size is too small for reliable background tasks"
msgstr ""
"El tamaño del paquete MySQL es demasiado pequeño para tareas en segundo "
"plano fiables"

#. translators: 1: current packet size (e.g. "1 MB"), 2: recommended floor (e.g. "4 MB")
#: .tmp-wporg/structura/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:134
#: plugin/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:134
msgid ""
"Your MySQL server reports <code>max_allowed_packet = %1$s</code>. Structura "
"queues background tasks (image generation, campaign steps) in the "
"<code>wp_actionscheduler_actions</code> table, and rows can exceed this "
"limit on a busy site. When that happens the task is silently dropped and you "
"see no featured image and no error. We recommend at least <strong>%2$s</"
"strong>. Most shared hosts will raise this on request."
msgstr ""
"Tu servidor MySQL indica <code>max_allowed_packet = %1$s</code>. Structura "
"encola tareas en segundo plano (generación de imágenes, pasos de campaña) en "
"la tabla <code>wp_actionscheduler_actions</code> y las filas pueden exceder "
"este límite en un sitio con mucha actividad. Cuando eso ocurre, la tarea se "
"descarta silenciosamente y no verás ni imagen destacada ni error. "
"Recomendamos al menos <strong>%2$s</strong>. La mayoría de los alojamientos "
"compartidos lo aumentan si lo solicitas."

#: .tmp-wporg/structura/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:145
#: plugin/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:145
msgid "MySQL packet size is sufficient for background tasks"
msgstr "El tamaño del paquete MySQL es suficiente para tareas en segundo plano"

#. translators: %s: current packet size
#: .tmp-wporg/structura/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:148
#: plugin/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:148
msgid ""
"Your MySQL server reports <code>max_allowed_packet = %s</code>, which is "
"large enough for Structura's background task queue."
msgstr ""
"Tu servidor MySQL indica <code>max_allowed_packet = %s</code>, suficiente "
"para la cola de tareas en segundo plano de Structura."

#: .tmp-wporg/structura/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:174
#: plugin/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:174
msgid "WordPress cron is disabled — verify your system cron is configured"
msgstr ""
"El cron de WordPress está desactivado — verifica que tu cron del sistema "
"esté configurado"

#: .tmp-wporg/structura/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:175
#: plugin/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:175
msgid ""
"Your <code>wp-config.php</code> sets <code>DISABLE_WP_CRON</code> to true. "
"Structura's background tasks (image generation, scheduled campaigns) rely on "
"Action Scheduler, which requires <strong>either</strong> WP-Cron <strong>or</"
"strong> a system cron job hitting <code>wp-cron.php</code>. If you don't "
"have a system cron set up, queued image tasks will never run."
msgstr ""
"Tu <code>wp-config.php</code> establece <code>DISABLE_WP_CRON</code> en "
"true. Las tareas en segundo plano de Structura (generación de imágenes, "
"campañas programadas) dependen de Action Scheduler, que requiere <strong>o "
"bien</strong> WP-Cron <strong>o bien</strong> una tarea cron del sistema que "
"acceda a <code>wp-cron.php</code>. Si no tienes un cron del sistema "
"configurado, las tareas de imágenes en cola nunca se ejecutarán."

#: .tmp-wporg/structura/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:183
#: plugin/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:183
msgid "WordPress cron is enabled"
msgstr "El cron de WordPress está activado"

#: .tmp-wporg/structura/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:184
#: plugin/includes/Core/Site_Health.php:184
msgid "Structura's background tasks can be dispatched via WP-Cron."
msgstr ""
"Las tareas en segundo plano de Structura se pueden despachar a través de WP-"
"Cron."

